<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Failed - TheLitStore</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #fff; color: #333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
        .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 40px 30px; background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
        .failed-icon { font-size: 60px; color: #e74c3c; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .desc { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .try-again-btn { background: #d73333; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 30px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; }
        .try-again-btn:hover { background: #b32929; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="failed-icon">&#10060;</div>
        <div class="title">Order Failed</div>
        <div class="desc">Your payment was not successful.<br>Do you want to try again?</div>
        <a href="/checkout"><button class="try-again-btn">Try Again</button></a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 